wikipedia_page.main: Victoria Claire Harwood Butler-Sloss is a British-born voice actress based in the United States. She works for anime roles at Geneon Entertainment/New Generation Pictures.

response: *Hon. William Edmund Minchin Patchell Butler-Sloss (b. 21 September 1967, d. 13 March 2018); married Victoria Harwood, a voice actress and author. William died of stomach cancer in 2018 at the age of 50. He was survived by two children and his widow.
